              <description><![CDATA[<p>If you have a learning design you would like to share and discuss with others, please set up a Cloud and then attach it to this Cloudscape: <a href="http://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloudscape/view/2122">Sharing Learning Designs</a>.</p>
